text.div:
This code system https://example.org/fhir/CodeSystem/CatPatientBreed defines the following codes:

CodeDisplayDefinition
domestic DomesticDomestic cat breed.
siamese SiameseSiamese cat breed.
persian PersianPersian cat breed with long hair and a round face.
siberian SiberianSiberian cat breed with a long, thick coat and a bush tail.
british_shorthair British ShorthairBritish Shorthair cat breed with a round face and a dense coat.
russian_blue Russian BlueRussian Blue cat breed with a short, dense coat and a plush blue-gray color.
muchkin MunchkinMunchkin cat breed with short legs.
ragdoll RagdollRagdoll cat breed with a semi-long coat and blue eyes.
birman BirmanBirman cat breed with a long, silky coat and deep blue eyes.
other OtherAny other breed not included in the list.

name: CatPatientBreed
title: Cat Patient Breed Code System
purpose: This FHIR resource type CodeSystem has been created for educational purposes.
